As for the men, the leaſt ſaid about them is the beſt;
and, as for their manners, egad! I never was treated with ſo much
ill-manners, by any other ſet of people, before or ſince!

Think no more of your falſe lover, Madam. Take my advice;
and, from among the noble youths of Florence, who languiſh for your
ſmiles, chuſe one to whom I may reſign you.
